{
  "info": {
    "name": "Form Filler API - Switchbox Handoff",
    "description": "Complete endpoint collection matching all real API routes. Import docs/formfiller.postman_environment.json, then set real Switchbox-owned current values in Postman before running. Signature, submit, and finalize are backend-enforced: /sign requires complete application data, /submit requires a complete signed application, and /finalize requires a complete submitted application plus at least one bank statement PDF before Switchbox delivery is queued. Do not add private internal admin/export values to this collection.",
